Saravia L.A. 2014 Neutral: A sofwtware to simulate spatially explicit neutral/hierarchical models  <http://dx.doi.org/10.6084/m9.figshare.969692>.  The last version can be found at <https://github.com/lsaravia/Neutral>

The model was used in:

1. Saravia, L.A. (2015). A new method to analyze species abundances in space using generalized dimensions. PeerJ Preprints., 3, e1321.